description: This table represents details of CHP (Child Health Plus) insurance. Child Health Plus provides free or low-cost health insurance for children under the age of 19 who are not eligible for Medicaid, coverage for children. All children receive their health care through a managed care plan. There are no immigration requirements for Child Health Plus.
